<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In Locale/Format.php, line 1140:</p>

<p>$options['date_format'] = self::getDateFormat($options['locale']);</p>

<p>$options may not contain a 'locale' element at this point, generating an E_NOTICE.</p>

<p>This will resolve to NULL which will be handled correctly further down the call chain (use application's default locale instead), so the problem is only the E_NOTICE itself.</p>

